description:
This course is all about preparing yourself for taking the AWS certified solutions architect- Associate Level Certification.

This course is designed with easy to understand explanations of the concepts but keeping the AWS terminology intact unlike several other courses out there. This course also emphasizes on all the key points in the form of Exam Tips which will make it easy for the aspirant to recollect important concepts before appearing for the exam.

In this course, you would find more than 40 Lectures with approximately 6 hours of to the point videos covering theoretical knowledge with the practical demonstration. The course comes with more than 150 practice questions to prepare you for the final exam.

This course is self-paced course and can be taken at any speed.

You should take this course if you are looking forward to be an AWS Certified Solutions Architect.
title: AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Associate Level Training
